data.description:
NORTH PORT ESTATES - Immaculate 3/2/2 on large private lot North of I-75. This home has been completely redone with tile floors through-out, window coverings & fixtures. Large principal rooms. Separate dining area. Double walk-out from great room to covered patio. Walk-out from master bedroom. Large master bath with with spacious separate shower and soaker tub. Master walk-in closets. Fans in all rooms. Newer appliances. 1st, & security required. Long term lease for ideal tenant.

(RLNE2913862)
